683
00:37:00,520 --> 00:37:02,900
Anping was arrogant.

684
00:37:03,200 --> 00:37:05,900
But he wasn't reckless.

685
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:09,580
Without striving for a higher position,

686
00:37:10,200 --> 00:37:12,580
